    <main>

        <section class="page-hero">

            <p class="eyebrow">Customer Care</p>

            <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

            <p>
                Learn more about our luxury raw hair, textures, lengths,
                wigs, HD lace, coloring, care, shipping, pickup, and exchanges.
            </p>

        </section>

        <div class="faq-layout">

            <aside class="faq-menu">

                <h2>FAQ Categories</h2>

                <a href="#hair-quality">Hair Quality</a>
                <a href="#origins-textures">Origins and Textures</a>
                <a href="#lengths-wigs">Lengths and Wigs</a>
                <a href="#coloring-care">Coloring and Care</a>
                <a href="#orders-shipping">Orders and Shipping</a>
                <a href="#pickup">Local Pickup</a>
                <a href="#returns">Returns and Exchanges</a>
                <a href="#hair-care-products">Hair-Care Products</a>

            </aside>

            <article>

                <section class="faq-section" id="hair-quality">

                    <h2>Hair Quality</h2>

                    <details open>
                        <summary>What type of hair does Big Boss Bundles sell?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Big Boss Bundles specializes in premium raw and
                            luxury human hair sourced from distinct hair origins.
                            Our hair is selected for softness, movement,
                            versatility, and long-lasting quality.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>How long does Big Boss Bundles hair last?</summary>

                        <p>
                            With proper installation, maintenance, washing,
                            conditioning, storage, and styling, Big Boss Bundles
                            hair can last for several years.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Does the hair shed?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Some shedding is normal with human hair products.
                            Proper installation, gentle detangling, limited
                            product buildup, and proper maintenance help reduce
                            unnecessary shedding.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Is the hair reusable?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Yes. With proper care, bundles, wigs, closures,
                            and frontals may be washed, maintained, stored,
                            and reused.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                </section>

                <section class="faq-section" id="origins-textures">

                    <h2>Hair Origins and Textures</h2>

                    <details>
                        <summary>What hair origins are available?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Big Boss Bundles offers five primary hair origins:
                        </p>

                        <ul>
                            <li>LAOS Premium Luxury Hair</li>
                            <li>Cambodian Raw Hair</li>
                            <li>Vietnamese Hair</li>
                            <li>Indian Raw Hair</li>
                            <li>Burmese Hair</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Which collection is the premium luxury collection?</summary>

                        <p>
                            The LAOS Collection is the Big Boss Bundles
                            Premium Luxury Collection.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>What textures are available?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Available textures may include:
                        </p>

                        <ul>
                            <li>Straight</li>
                            <li>Kinky Straight</li>
                            <li>Body Wave</li>
                            <li>Deep Wave</li>
                            <li>Curly</li>
                            <li>Kinky Curly</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p>
                            Availability may vary by hair origin and product type.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Will raw hair look exactly identical every time?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Raw hair is a natural product. Minor variations in
                            color, texture, curl pattern, wave pattern, and
                            fullness may occur between bundles and orders.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                </section>

                <section class="faq-section" id="lengths-wigs">

                    <h2>Lengths, Wigs, Closures, and Frontals</h2>

                    <details>
                        <summary>What bundle lengths are available?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Bundle lengths generally range from 12 inches
                            through 32 inches. Available lengths may vary by
                            hair origin and current inventory.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>How long are the wigs?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Wig lengths may be available up to 40 inches,
                            depending on the hair origin, texture, density,
                            and current availability.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>What wig densities are available?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Wig density options may include:
                        </p>

                        <ul>
                            <li>180%</li>
                            <li>200%</li>
                            <li>230%</li>
                            <li>250%</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Are your wigs, closures, and frontals HD lace?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Yes. All Big Boss Bundles wigs, closures,
                            and frontals include HD lace.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>What lace sizes are available?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Lace sizes may include 13×4 and 13×6 for applicable
                            wigs and frontals. Available lace options will appear
                            in the product dropdown menu.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>How do I select texture, length, density, or lace size?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Each product page will include dropdown menus for
                            the options available for that product. The price
                            will update based on the selected product options.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                </section>

                <section class="faq-section" id="coloring-care">

                    <h2>Coloring, Styling, and Hair Care</h2>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Can the hair be colored?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Yes. Big Boss Bundles premium raw hair can be
                            professionally colored and lifted up to 613 blonde.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Can the hair be curled or straightened?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Yes. The hair may be curled, straightened,
                            and restyled. Use heat protectant and avoid
                            excessive heat.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Should I use a professional stylist?</summary>

                        <p>
                            We recommend using a licensed professional for
                            installation, bleaching, coloring, cutting,
                            customization, and significant texture changes.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>How should I care for the hair?</summary>

                        <ul>
                            <li>Wash the hair gently as needed.</li>
                            <li>Use a moisturizing conditioner.</li>
                            <li>Detangle carefully from the ends upward.</li>
                            <li>Avoid excessive product buildup.</li>
                            <li>Use heat protectant before applying heat.</li>
                            <li>Store the hair properly when not in use.</li>
                            <li>Protect curls and waves while sleeping.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Does the hair require a lot of product?</summary>

                        <p>
                            No. Minimal product is recommended. Too much product
                            may cause buildup, reduce movement, and make the hair
                            feel heavy.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                </section>

                <section class="faq-section" id="orders-shipping">

                    <h2>Orders and Shipping</h2>

                    <details>
                        <summary>How long does it take to receive an order?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Orders not immediately available generally require
                            approximately 7 to 10 business days for processing
                            and fulfillment. Shipping transit time begins after
                            the carrier receives the package.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Will I receive tracking information?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Yes, when tracking is available. Tracking may be
                            sent by email, text message, customer account,
                            or the marketplace used to place the order.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Is signature confirmation required?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Big Boss Bundles may require signature confirmation
                            to protect customers and reduce delivery fraud.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Can I change my shipping address?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Address changes are not guaranteed after an order
                            is submitted. Contact Big Boss Bundles immediately
                            if a correction is needed.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Do you sell on other platforms?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Big Boss Bundles may also sell through TikTok Shop,
                            Amazon, Facebook Shop, and other approved official
                            retail channels.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                </section>

                <section class="faq-section" id="pickup">

                    <h2>Local Pickup</h2>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Is local pickup available?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Yes. Local pickup may be available at:
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            <strong>
                                301 W Pecan Street<br>
                                Pflugerville, TX 78660
                            </strong>
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Can I arrive as soon as I place my order?</summary>

                        <p>
                            No. Customers must call ahead and wait for
                            confirmation that the order is ready before arriving.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>What do I need to bring for pickup?</summary>

                        <p>
                            You may be asked to show identification, order
                            confirmation, payment verification, or written
                            authorization if another person is picking up
                            your order.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                </section>

                <section class="faq-section" id="returns">

                    <h2>Returns and Exchanges</h2>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Do you offer refunds?</summary>

                        <p>
                            All sales are final. Big Boss Bundles does not
                            offer refunds or returns because of change of mind,
                            preference, incorrect customer selection,
                            installation, coloring, cutting, alteration, or use.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Can I request an exchange?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Eligible exchange requests must be submitted within
                            five calendar days after receiving the order.
                            Approval is subject to the Return and Exchange Policy.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>What condition must the product be in?</summary>

                        <p>
                            The product must remain unused, unworn,
                            uninstalled, unwashed, uncolored, uncut,
                            unaltered, and in its original condition
                            with original packaging and ties intact.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>Can opened hair-care products be exchanged?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Hair-care and personal-care products generally
                            cannot be exchanged after the seal is broken,
                            the container is opened, or the product is used.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                </section>

                <section class="faq-section" id="hair-care-products">

                    <h2>Celebrity Collection Products</h2>

                    <details>
                        <summary>How much is the Edge Control?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Big Boss Bundles Edge Control is $14.99.
                            It provides strong hold with no white residue
                            and no flaking.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>How much are the Melting Spray and Wax Stick?</summary>

                        <p>
                            The Melting Spray is $11.99 and the Wax Stick
                            is $11.99.
                        </p>
                    </details>

                    <details>
                        <summary>How much is the Lace Tint Mousse?</summary>

                        <p>
                            Lace Tint Mousse is $10.99 and is available in
